#define gc getchar_unlocked

void scanint(int &x)
{
    register long int c = gc();
    x = 0;
    for(;(c<48 || c>57);c = gc());
    for(;c>47 && c<58;c = gc()) {x = (x<<1) + (x<<3) + c - 48;}
}


struct node{
    int val;
	node *nxt;
}*top=NULL,* bottom =NULL;

void push(int val){
	node *p = new node();
	p->nxt = NULL;
	p->val =val;
	if(top==NULL){
		top=p;
		bottom = p;
	}
	else if(val<top->val){
		p->nxt = top;
		top = p;
	}
	else if(val>bottom->val){
		bottom ->nxt = p;
		bottom=p;
	}
	else{
		node *q =top, *r = top->nxt;
		while( r !=NULL && val>r->val){
			q = r;
			r = r->nxt;
		}
		q ->nxt = p;
		p->nxt = r;
	}
}

void display(){
	node *a = top;
	while(a!=NULL){
		if(a->nxt !=NULL)
			printf("%d\n",a->val);
		else
			printf("%d",a->val);
		a = a->nxt;
	}
}
